---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import EmailCapture from "../../components/EmailCapture.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Episode 01 — Multi-Channel Sales Sync · Gerard Agba"
  description="The free n8n workflow that reconciles Shopify, Amazon, Faire, PayPal and Klarna in 12 minutes."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-12">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-4">
      Episode 01 · Multi-Channel Sales Sync
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">
      The free n8n workflow that reconciles Shopify, Amazon, Faire, PayPal and Klarna in 12 minutes.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mt-6 max-w-2xl">
      Built for DTC brands doing $2&ndash;15M ARR who spend 25+ hours a month closing their
      books across 4+ sales channels.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- VIDEO -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-black">
      <!-- Replace YOUTUBE_VIDEO_ID after you upload -->
      <iframe
        class="w-full h-full"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tDMpYcph4mo"
        title="Episode 01 — Multi-Channel Sales Sync"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mt-3 italic">
      71 transactions · $304K in revenue · 16 anomalies surfaced &mdash; using only n8n. No paid SaaS.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- THE PAIN -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">If your books look like this, the workflow is for you</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-4 text-[color:var(--color-fg)]">
      <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] font-bold">→</span> <span><strong>25&ndash;35 hours/month</strong> manually pulling CSVs from Shopify, Amazon, Faire, PayPal, Klarna.</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] font-bold">→</span> <span>Channel fees, refunds, chargebacks living in <strong>5 different formats</strong>.</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] font-bold">→</span> <span>Cross-period accruals and FX revaluations caught only by your bookkeeper at month-end.</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)] font-bold">→</span> <span>No single source of truth when your CFO asks <em>&ldquo;what&rsquo;s our real net revenue?&rdquo;</em></span></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT YOU GET -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What you get</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[color:var(--color-card)] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-xs text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-2">01</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">The n8n JSON</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">40 nodes, ready to import into self-hosted or cloud n8n.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[color:var(--color-card)] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-xs text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-2">02</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Setup guide (PDF, 8 pages)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Credentials, file paths, and where to plug in your own data.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[color:var(--color-card)] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-xs text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-2">03</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">5-min Loom walkthrough</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Me importing it into a blank n8n and running it end-to-end.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[color:var(--color-card)] border border-white/5">
        <div class="text-xs text-[color:var(--color-accent)] mb-2">04</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">6 sample CSVs</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Test on Lumen demo data before connecting your real channels.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DOWNLOADS -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-12">
    <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-[color:var(--color-card)] border border-white/5">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Download the workflow</h3>
      <p class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mb-6">Free. No email required.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/downloads/multi-channel-sales-sync.zip"
          class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[color:var(--color-accent)] text-black font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition"
          download
        >
          Workflow (ZIP) →
        </a>
        <a
          href="/downloads/multi-channel-sales-sync-setup-guide.pdf"
          class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-white/15 hover:border-white/40 transition"
        >
          Setup guide (PDF)
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEWSLETTER -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <EmailCapture
      heading="Know when the next episode drops"
      subheading="One email per new workflow. Nothing else."
      tag="newsletter"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Who&rsquo;s behind this?</h2>
    <p class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
      I&rsquo;m Gerard. I build n8n workflows that automate the boring, expensive parts of
      running a DTC brand&rsquo;s finance stack &mdash; reconciliation, fee audits, cash-flow
      forecasting. Every episode of this channel breaks down one real problem and ships
      the workflow free. If you want it built for your stack, I do that too.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- SOFT CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-16 mb-24">
    <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10">
      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Want this set up on your actual data?</h3>
      <p class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mb-5 max-w-xl">
        I install and customize this workflow for DTC brands doing $2&ndash;15M ARR.
        Fixed-scope, fixed-price, done in 2 weeks.
      </p>
      <a href="/work-with-me" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white text-black font-semibold hover:bg-white/90 transition">
        Book a 20-min call →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
